data/raw/qm9/*.part
data/raw/qm9/extracted/
!data/raw/qm9/qm9.sdf.csv
!data/raw/zinc/
data/raw/zinc/*
!data/raw/zinc/zinc15_250K_2D.csv
data/processed/
results/**
